Package: TRskim
Type: Package
Title: TRskim: Tandem repeat motif visualizer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nour", "Hassan", , "nour.hassan@mail.utoronto.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Nour Hassan <nour.hassan@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: TRskim is an R package that visualizes tandem repeat composition by 
  decomposing sequences into known/novel motifs, aligning them, and generating 
  tile plots to compare motif patterns across alleles.
